wikipedia_page.main: George Page (30 November 1898 – 1931) was an English footballer who made 149 appearances in the Football League playing for Barnsley, Ashington, Accrington Stanley, Lincoln City and Crewe Alexandra. He played as a left back. He also played in the Midland League for York City.
